The paper discusses security vulnerabilities in the GSM network and proposes a new secure application layer protocol for SMS messages to be used in m-payment systems. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of cryptography (cs.CR), security and privacy (cs.CY), software engineering (cs.SE), information theory (cs.IT), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI).
